Class DatabaseDataManager<I,T extends DataObject<I>>

java.lang.Object
com.bws.jdistil.core.datasource.database.DatabaseDataManager<I,T>

Direct Known Subclasses:
BoundDatabaseDataManager
public abstract class DatabaseDataManager<I,T extends DataObject<I>> extends Object implements IDataManager<I,T>
Abstract database data manager class implementing a portion of the IDataManager interface.

Bryan Snipes
